# =============================================================================
# ClawBench Agent Configuration Example — Codex Backend
# ClawBench 智能体配置示例 — Codex 后端
# =============================================================================
#
# OpenAI Codex CLI — supports custom profiles for different model backends.
# OpenAI Codex CLI — 支持通过 profile 切换不同的模型后端。
#
# Model discovery: Codex CLI does not support listing models via CLI command.
# Models must be manually specified in the `models` field.
# 模型发现：Codex CLI 不支持通过命令列出模型，需在 models 字段手动指定。
#
# Use the `command` field to pass profile arguments to the Codex CLI.
# 使用 command 字段可以向 Codex CLI 传递 profile 参数。
#
# This file is NOT loaded (the .yaml.example extension is ignored by LoadAgents).
# 本文件不会被加载（.yaml.example 后缀会被 LoadAgents 忽略）。
# To use, copy as e.g. my-codex-agent.yaml and modify the config.
# 实际使用时请复制为如 my-codex-agent.yaml 并修改配置。
# =============================================================================

id: codex
name: Codex
icon: 🤠
specialty: OpenAI Codex CLI 编码助手（MiniMax 后端）
backend: codex
thinking_effort_levels:
  - low
  - medium
  - high
models:
  - id: codex-MiniMax-M2.7
    name: MiniMax M2.7
    default: true
command: codex --profile m27
system_prompt: |
  You are a coding assistant using OpenAI Codex CLI. Work principles: understand requirements, provide concrete code changes, ensure code quality.

# thinking_effort [optional]: Default thinking effort level when user hasn't selected one.
# 留空或不设置 = 自动（不传 -c model_reasoning_effort= 参数）。用户在前端选择后会覆盖此默认值。
# thinking_effort: high
